# Inventory Management

## Description
Inventory Management is a web application used to manage shop items, stock, customers, and billing.
It helps shopkeepers reduce manual work and handle daily shop operations easily.

## Features
- Item and stock management
- Customer management
- Bill generation
- Purchase history tracking

## User Roles

### Shopkeeper
- Add, update, and delete items
- View stock details
- Generate bills

### Customer
- View available items
- Place orders
- View bills and purchase history

## Technologies
- Python
- Django
- MySQL / SQLite
- HTML, CSS, Bootstrap

## System Requirements
- Python installed
- Django framework
- Database (MySQL or SQLite)

## Project Use
This project is developed for learning and academic purposes.
